Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:35.80,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Deje sa niečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.42,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Už to povedz.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:40.93,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čo ak...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:46.60,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čo by si robila, keby som zomrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.27,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ty trdlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.03,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nehovor také divné veci!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:03.87,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Rodičia by sa uplakali k smrti,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.66,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,ak by si zomrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:09.33,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dokonca aj ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:14.29,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tak mi nehovor, že zomrieš, dobre?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:16.13,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:18.59,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:22.93,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ozaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:28.85,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Povedzme otcovi a mame o všetkom, čo sme prežili, keď prídeme domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:32.48,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poviem im, že si sa snažil a dal do toho všetko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:37.15,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,A ja im poviem to isté o tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:40.74,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Stále musíme dať mame jej darček
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.61,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,a povedať, že si jej ho vybral ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:48.54,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čoskoro budeme doma, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:51.79,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.92,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Letné prázdniny ešte len začali,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:58.13,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,tak si ich poriadne užime, keď sa veci dajú do poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:02.47,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Obzvlášť si ich užime, keďže som sa minulý rok a ten pred tým musela pripravovať na vstupné testy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.30,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Presne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:10.81,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vtedy som ti závidela, že sa nemusíš učiť,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:16.56,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,ale pre teba to musela byť tiež nuda, pretože som ťa nikam nemohla zobrať.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.61,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ani nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:19.32,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bol som s Itsukim,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:24.91,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,a okrem toho, bol som veľmi rád, keď si mi nakreslila pár obrázkov žiab.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.16,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tebe sa tie šmatlanice naozaj páčili?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.54,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,To neboli šmatlanice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.37,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale boli!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.21,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Boli pekné!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.38,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ty si divný, Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.31,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pozri sa, Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.10,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,To je kôň! { A rozpráva!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:57.98,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.03,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Skús ho jemne pohladkať.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.57,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Z času na čas sa sem vráťme.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:06.45,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.75,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki, už sme skoro tam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:20.59,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:28.05,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nebýva tamto tvoj kamarát?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.14,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Býva.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.39,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,To je dom Kazuho.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:35.14,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Kto vie, či je náš dom v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:03.55,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.17,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.43,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.60,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.01,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vďakabohu, že si v poriadku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.14,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ty tiež, Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.56,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vďaka bohu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.19,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mayu, ty—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.81,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,N-No tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.11,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bože, Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.03,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prestaň.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:29.66,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nemohla som sa s nikým spojiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.07,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Keď som sa spýtala tvojej mamy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:33.70,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,povedala, že nevie, čo sa vám stalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:37.04,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Stretla si sa s mojou mamou, Mayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:37.66,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:40.54,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Stretli sme sa v úkryte v základnej škole;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.92,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,sú tam aj s tvojim otcom,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:47.26,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,ale povedala, že ste šli sami do Odaiby,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:49.93,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,a nemohla sa s vami spojiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:51.55,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.31,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Takže mama a otec sú v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.51,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:59.56,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoj otec sa zranil v práci, \Nale nie je to nič vážne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:03.15,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoja mama sa o vás naozaj bála.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.44,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vďaka, že si mi dala vedieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:08.53,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,V tvojej rodine sú všetci v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.32,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno, sú v pohode.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.62,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Boli sme všetci doma, keď sa to stalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:16.41,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Sme tu, keďže mama bude čochvíľa rodiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:18.70,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vďakabohu, že sú všetci v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.00,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:23.00,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nemohla som sa ale spojiť s Yukou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:26.46,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,A tiež nevieme, čo sa stalo \Ns ostatnými spolužiakmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.76,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Videla som Megu pred dvoma dňami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:36.26,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Jej matka zomrela.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.77,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Kto vie, čo sa stane teraz.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.86,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Myslíš si, že sa znova začne učiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:52.66,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Okrem toho, kde je tvoj brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.32,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Č-Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:56.28,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ešte pred chvíľou tu bol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.29,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:01.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,No nič, som rada, že ste v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:04.75,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mali by ste si pohnúť a ísť do základky.\N Rodičia na vás už čakajú.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:05.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:07.59,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Maj sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.25,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čau, čau!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.88,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,Pozriem sa, ako sa vám darí, keď sato tu upokojí, dobre?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:13.09,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prečo si—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:16.76,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bež! {yabaizo!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:19.18,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,No len počkajte,\N keď sa mi dostanete do rúk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.61,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.98,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nepovedala som ti, že nemáš utekať?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.32,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poďme, Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.12,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Kam to bežíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.12,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Do školy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.80,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.22,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Povedala som, počkaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.18,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bože.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:20.87,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:23.83,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,To si ty, závisláčka na telefóne!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.17,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tak by si ma nemal volať.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:28.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Moje meno je Mirai, spomínaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.54,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:30.71,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.09,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Itsuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.05,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nevidel si tu Yuukiho?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.88,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pred chvíľou tadeto prešiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:37.76,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.84,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:40.22,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.64,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Počuli sme, že je tu mama s otcom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.14,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tak to potom asi šiel do telocvične.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:48.85,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoja mama a všetci ostatní sú tam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:54.44,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Sú všetci z tvojej rodiny v poriadku, Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:55.11,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:57.07,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale tvoj domov je úplne zničený.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:57.86,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:58.66,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:12.25,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Kde je moja mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.09,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tamto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.35,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nemyslím si, že tu je.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.44,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.57,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Videla si tu Yuukiho mamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:38.49,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:44.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pred chvíľou šla domov po nové oblečenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:48.62,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Myslím, že tvoj otec je stále v nemocnici.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:49.46,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,V nemocnici?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:53.34,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, ale povedala, že to nie je vážne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.80,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Takže by mal byť v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.84,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoja mama mala o teba vážny strach,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:01.47,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,tak rýchlo za ňou utekaj a ukáž jej, že si v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:04.43,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mohla by si ju dobehnúť, ak vyrazíš ihneď.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:05.68,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prečo za ňou nejdeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:06.68,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Idem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:09.69,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pôjdem hneď domov, keď nájdem Yuukiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.27,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:16.44,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.28,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:23.07,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tak už nám zostáva iba ihrisko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:32.62,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mám pocit, ako keby sme to zasadili\N veľmi dávno, ale neviem prečo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:41.55,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mohol by sa tu ukázať, ak tu počkáme.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.34,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:51.73,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.36,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:03.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.45,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bože, to decko je ale prípad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:08.70,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Počkaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:28.64,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Chcel som dať Yuukimu náš gaštanový denník.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.48,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Gaštanový denník?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.18,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Presne.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.73,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je to náš denník pozorovaní.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.65,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki mal napísať ďalší zápis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:38.07,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nevedela som, že si vediete o ňom denník.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:39.69,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:42.74,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bol to Yuukiho nápad, aby sme ho písali spolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.24,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.07,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.83,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.16,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.88,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:04.17,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bože, Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.72,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prečo stále utekáš, bez toho aby si mi dal vedieť kam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.43,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Všade som ťa hľadala.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:09.18,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.72,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáč, {\i1}sestrička.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:12.68,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:15.10,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:17.52,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Našla si ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.36,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:20.36,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki, mal by si povedať Itsukimu, že si—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.86,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Č-Čo to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.82,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Možno šiel na toaletu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:28.37,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Naše toalety sú dosť špinavé.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.33,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Sú veľmi odporné.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:33.00,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Toto je naša trieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:34.37,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tuto sedávam ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:37.37,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,A tu zase Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.80,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Sú tak malé.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.22,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nespomínam si, že by boli až {\i1}takéto{\i0}malé.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.76,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,A tiež to tu počmáral.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.47,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ten Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.23,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:59.35,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tiež sme tu si vystavili obrázky, ktoré sme nakreslili.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:00.48,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vidíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.45,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tento nakreslil Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:18.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Keď som bola v prvej triede, išla som s celou rodinou po moste v Odaibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.38,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bola to zábava.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.92,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki Onozawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.05,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:30.22,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki mi hovoril, že by sa tam chcel vrátiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:39.27,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(5088,6130,\c&HF7F7F7&\3c&HF7F7F7&\4c&HF7F7F7&)}Chcel som ísť do Odaiby, pretože som chcel s tebou vidieť most.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:44.65,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:46.28,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prečo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:48.90,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.28,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,To je divné.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:51.70,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prečo mi je...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.79,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Idem pohľadať Yuukiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.21,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prečo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.67,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prečo plačem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:10.68,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:14.85,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prečo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:18.31,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Neplač, {\i1}sestrička.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:21.31,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Som tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:23.81,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:29.82,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bože.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:33.16,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Naštvem sa, ak ešte raz odídeš bez toho, aby si mi to povedal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:39.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Zdá sa, že dnešné deti majú dobré písmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.96,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Môžeš povedať, ktoré je moje?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.33,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tak sa na to pozrime...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:45.21,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Našla som to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.21,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.67,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Píšem pekne, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:50.67,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Napísal si to až príliš veľké.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:54.30,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale dal si tomu všetko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.97,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je to na tom vidieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.93,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Som predsa tvoja sestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:15:58.93,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:01.89,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Veľmi sa mi páči tvoje meno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:08.28,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki nebol na toalete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:10.07,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.78,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Celú dobu bol —
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:16.32,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Č-Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:18.62,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bol tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:23.92,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ten Yuuki na mieste neobstojí ani chvíľu, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:28.71,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vždy sa niekde potuluje a potom sa stratí...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:35.68,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:38.93,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Idem po ten denník.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:41.93,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bývam blízko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.77,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Počkaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:45.31,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Idem s tebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.90,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Aj tak musím nájsť mamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:50.65,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.07,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:55.20,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Som v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:55.91,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poďme.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:57.49,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:16.59,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:19.10,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vezmime ten denník niekedy inokedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.10,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vo vnútri to je nebezpečné, vráť sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.02,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Neboj sa, bol som tu aj ráno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.44,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Kde je Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:30.73,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Idem po Itsukiho, {\i1}sestrička.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.44,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:32.73,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:34.32,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vráť sa sem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.40,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bože.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:37.66,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.78,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,To je v pohode, tak sa vráť.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.28,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ešte chvíľku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:42.74,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tu je.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:45.12,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nech sa páči.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:48.17,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Daj to za mňa Yuukimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:48.92,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.47,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,20. Júl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:58.22,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dnes som zasadil gaštan s Itsukim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:01.72,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sestrička{\i0} z nejakého dôvodu nazýva gaštany ako makaróny.
