Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:15.99,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vďaka, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:18.74,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Určite mu to dám.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:19.49,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:21.20,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:24.20,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Kam si šiel tentokrát?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:27.00,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nebol to tvoj nápad ísť po Itsukiho?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.96,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čo si robil?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.83,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poď, ideme naspäť.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:32.29,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ty tiež, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:33.71,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ideš naspäť do úkrytu, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.05,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:39.05,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:40.43,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poď sem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:45.89,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.14,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
